FreetuxTV 0.6.0 (2011-22-11)
  - Alert on exit only when a channel is recording
  - Preference to set timeout when downloading with curl
  - Compilation with libnotify 0.7.x
  - Compilation with gtk3
  - Better display for recording list
  - Issue 23 : Hide original window when switching fullscreen mode
  - Show message dialog for player error
  - Issue 86 : Ability to program recording
  - Added TV channel logos:
      WebTV: Canal26, CanalRural, Canal4 SanJuan, Canal5 Tucuman, Canal10 Tucuman,
      	Canal6 Posadas, Canal9 EntreRios, Hit Music TV, Music plus Classic Rock, Music plus Hits,
        Music plus pop rock, Reservoir Films, Télévision savoir, TN, UrbaniaTV, Zona 31

FreetuxTV 0.5.2 (2011-01-10)
  - Added new official icon and splashcreen for FreetuxTV
  - Added proxy support: configuration in preferences window.
  - Created option --help to display FreetuxTV help.
  - Created option --open-channel to launch a channel through the command line.
  - Ability to suppress channel in favorites group.
  - Ability to reorder the groups in the channels list.
  - Add FreetuxTV's german and chinese simplified translation.
  - Added keyboard shorcut for fullscreen, volume control and play pause.
  - Added systray icon to hide/show FreetuxTV.
  - Dialog to show channel's properties.
  - Preference to allow use of the VLC configuration file for LibVLC.
  - No more group without results in the channel search.
  - Preference to ignore diacritics.
  - Added TV channel logos:
      WebTV: Orange Sport Infos, R King TV, Zahra TV, TV8 Moselle Est, Clap TV, Archeo TV,
         Canalmoza, CT2E, Hit Music TV, HiScore TV, Info Sport, Soleil TV, TVSF
      WebRadio: BBC, RNE, RAI, ChanteFrance, Radio O
  - Updating and adding playlists (See http://code.google.com/p/freetuxtv/wiki/MajListesChaines)

