FreetuxTV 0.4.0 (2009-12-11)
  - Migration to GtkBuilder, deprecate libglade.
  - Added panel to display recordings list and play it in FreetuxTV.
  - Preference to enable or disable desktop notifications.
  - Preferences to transcode recording in pre-configured formats.
  - Added menu to display and edit group properties.
  - Added tab in the add group window to easily add existing groups
    (WebTV, WebRadio, Webcam (depending to ISP (Internet Service Provider))
    or between one of the twenty availiable languages).
  - Ability to delete and refresh multiple groups at once.
  - Display number of installed channels.
