FreetuxTV 0.2.0 (2008-11-08)
  - Migration to libVLC 0.9.4.
  - Use of alternative VLC configuration file.

FreetuxTV 0.1.2 (2008-10-25)
  - Added TV channel logos: AB Moteurs, APTV, Artpla TV, Astro Center TV, ASTV, Babylon TV, La Locale, RMC
  - Added button play to restart the current playing channel, if stopped.
  - Support for multimedia keyboard hotkeys.
  - Support for redirection HTTP 302 to download playlist from Free.
  - Save application params in config file.
  - Added menu "Preferences".
  - Playing last channel on application startup.

FreetuxTV 0.1.1 (2008-07-20)
  - Fix bug segmentation fault on Mandriva/Debian
  - Removed empty tabs "En cours" and "Enregistrements".
  - Message on empty channel list to show how to load channels list.
  - Added version number on About window.

FreetuxTV 0.1.0 (2008-07-06)
  - First version.
  - Ability to play channels.
  - Fullscreen mode.
  - Channels groups.
  - Refresh from downloading the playlist of the group.
  - Auto-association of channel with its logo.
  - Dynamic search for channels.
  - Small mode.
